name: Sea to Sky Realty
tag_list: bradenton, sarasota, real-estate, realty, homes-for-sale, buyers-and-sellers, international, reo, short-sale
overview:
Sea to Sky Realty is the leading international Florida and California Real Estate network. Focusing on the need of the local sellers and the international Clientele it connects local Real Estate market with the global audience of buyers in the 21st century.

Sea to Sky Realty is member of the National and Florida Association of Realtors and Florida MLS. Sea to Sky Realty is connected with leading associates of national known brands, like Remax, Coldwell Banker, Century 21 and Sotheby’s International Realty and the best independent real estate brokerages.

Besides the residential market, Sea to Sky Realty is working as a relocation network, providing full service assistance for expediates from all over the world.

For international executives and company owners it offers help in obtaining the necessary immigration, tax and legal assistance thru the network.
